# SQL compatibility checker baseline — accepted/suppressed violations.
#
# Regenerated after the LIKE-wildcard ESCAPE-clause fix (issue #15 from the
# #241 adversarial review). All prior entries were stale: every LIKE site that
# feeds on user input now carries both escape_like() and an explicit ESCAPE
# clause, so SQL003/SQL004 produce zero violations repo-wide.
#
# To regenerate from the current tree:
#   python3 scripts/lint/sql_compat_checker.py --baseline > scripts/lint/.sql_baseline
